        INPUT:

        - ``item`` -- a hashable object; the item to add

        - ``value`` -- the value associated with ``item``

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: from sage.data_structures.pairing_heap import PairingHeap_of_n_hashables
            sage: P = PairingHeap_of_n_hashables(5)
            sage: P.push(1, 2)
            sage: P.top()
