            sage: from sage.data_structures.pairing_heap import PairingHeap_of_n_hashables
            sage: P = PairingHeap_of_n_hashables(2)
            sage: P.push(1, 2)
            sage: P.push(1, 2)
            Traceback (most recent call last):
            ...
